Package: pip-basic-depends
Version: 1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, python, build-essential, cmake, ninja, libopenblas, libandroid-execinfo, patchelf, binutils, rust, libxml2, libxslt
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://alienkrishn.page.gd
Description: Essential build dependencies for Python packages
 Provides all necessary build tools and libraries required for compiling
 Python packages with pip. This includes:
 - Compilation tools (build-essential, cmake, ninja)
 - Math libraries (libopenblas)
 - Android-specific libraries (libandroid-execinfo)
 - Binary utilities (patchelf, binutils)
 - Rust compiler for Rust-based Python extensions
 - Git for source code retrieval
 Ensures successful wheel building and package installation without errors.
